  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Because in this little city, where we get in the house, from the blanket cover I did, for my two sister, a dress, and myself-- you know, should look.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But we don't want to wait.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We went to Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Also the Joint help us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And what was the custom, people who survive-- either for a tree or someplace where you could-- you put your name there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So I cannot remember where be put the [INAUDIBLE] girl's name.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And my cousin, who was in Israel, who lived in Bratislava-- they went Budapest, and Bratislava-- back and forth-- because they heard we survived.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Because before us, people much earlier arrived to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And in Budapest, the Joint have a place, [INAUDIBLE], to people like us who arrived there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "They took our clothes, and it was [? lie on it ?] or-- or give something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this cousin of mine, where are we going to sleep?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, so they took us a private place to sleep.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the first meal, they-- they-- and next day, I remember where my fiance mother lived, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went there, by foot-- you know, we don't have no money to take-- and we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She give her apartment.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think we stayed there about 10 days, still, when they fixed my teeth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When did you find out what happened to your parents?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parent?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They don't come back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We heard, after, that everybody who went right-- if you facing your left-- you know, Mengele facing them left, right-- then went, same day-- some stories tell-- same day at the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some stories tell, the next day to the-- so that's the reason I keep shiva two days [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My sister decide that the first day in New York, somehow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
